Response:  Julia played with 11 kids on Monday and 12 kids on Tuesday. To find out how many more kids she played with on Tuesday than on Monday, we need to subtract the number of kids she played with on Monday from the number of kids she played with on Tuesday:

12 - 11 = 1
So, Julia played with 1 more kid on Tuesday than she did on Monday.;

